{
  "name": "RPlog_Headaches_and_Hangovers",
  "title": "Tracking Down a Hungover Archaeologist",
  "summary": "At the renovated Grand Palanhi Hotel, Shenner, Jessalyn, and Luke Skywalker track down the archaeologist Paul Nighman, prying his whereabouts from a bribe-seeking bellboy whom Luke nudges with a touch of the Force. They find Paul nursing a hangover in the casino, prickly and reluctant to share what he knows about ancient artifacts that the dealer Grathix uncovered on Mandalore. After tense exchanges and a private apology between Paul and Shenner, Lando Calrissian arrives complaining of a Mandalorian bounty hunter trailing him, and the group settles in to bargain. Paul reveals research suggesting Grathix may possess a Force-amplifying device left from the Jedi purges, and agrees to travel with Jessalyn and Shenner aboard the Black Dragon to investigate while Luke stays behind to face his own dangerous business. The meeting ends with arrangements made, Lando promising to fund the expedition, and Paul retiring to his room where, after a bath, he promptly falls asleep.",
